ads/2024/02/Astley-Wheatus@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Astley-Wheatus@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Astley-Wheatus@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Astley-Wheatus@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>一支乐队因分享<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rick-astley">Rick Astley</a>风格翻唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wheatus">Wheatus</a>的热门单曲《Teenage Dirtbag》而走红。看看下面。</p><p>本周早些时候（2 月 26 日），一支名为 Deco 的乐队在 Instagram 上分享了这段不寻常的混搭片段。</p><p>在视频中，主唱装扮成 Rick Astley，就像他在 1987 年的标志性歌曲《Never Gonna Give You Up》的音乐视频中一样，穿着同样的西装外套和条纹 T 恤。还添加了绿屏背景以创建与原始视频中相同的背景。</p><p>一旦乐器演奏了这首 80 年代的经典歌曲，这位歌手就会对阿斯特利做出惊人准确的印象，捕捉到他的动作和举止，但用 00 年代热门歌曲《Teenage Dirtbag》的歌词取代了歌曲的原始歌词。</p><p>看看下面。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C3x_MQNtJFZ/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/s